  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Open letter to heat network operators about consumer protection standards
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Open letter from Claire Perry to all heat network operators regarding a voluntary industry scheme to raise consumer protection standards.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

